{"tid":2191730,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇九龍區巴打係新手又想接觸足球? 想召集一齊練下波","createTime":"2020-09-06T15:23:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T04:33:25.000Z","uid":248481,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4fef09b0e6b9d72acf112a167cd2e78cec87120b","tid":2191730,"uid":248481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:23:10.000Z","msg":"小弟中學開始已經想學踢波, 奈何學校廢,冇咩契機學到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係大學時跟朋友衫尾踢過幾場,覺得好趣, 一直都想搵志同道合嘅巴打一齊由0開始接觸呢個運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以想召集新手一齊學踢波, 首選係九龍區(睇番邊區人數多)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新手嘅定義係<br />\n連波都控唔定<br />\n傳球都會撻Q<br />\n希望可搵到一齊出黎練波/體能<br />\n疫情之後約出黎搵個球場<br />\n大家互相傳下波斬下波<br />\n練下點樣控球<br />\n<br />\n我希望新手同老手比例可以 7:3<br />\n<br />\n利申: 本人對足球認知好低 希望有有心老手巴打carry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n填表: 會加你入gp <br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/5pYX8Dc5HXcoXiFSA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F5pYX8Dc5HXcoXiFSA&d=uo2GI0poDlFkSsUZ5iwE4gOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=136edeea\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/5pYX8Dc5HXcoXiFSA</a>"},{"pid":"49dd204b614e427ed7d521d7e949a3100adf5af8","tid":2191730,"uid":164004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:29:46.000Z","msg":"出到黎個個美斯"},{"pid":"d8e6d4cdc183969af308f5db7be89cfb7e494e35","tid":2191730,"uid":174013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:33:41.000Z","msg":"次次依D GROUP都會有班踢過學屆比賽，踢過乜乜區隊，又或者跟過乜乜足球訓練學校<br />\n然後無踢一排就話自己係新手要JOIN"},{"pid":"78712d8131fbcfb56f3405c30d26832e675d0c84","tid":2191730,"uid":248481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8e6d4cdc183969af308f5db7be89cfb7e494e35","tid":2191730,"uid":174013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:33:41.000Z","msg":"次次依D GROUP都會有班踢過學屆比賽，踢過乜乜區隊，又或者跟過乜乜足球訓練學校<br />\n然後無踢一排就話自己係新手要JOIN"